<L N="47">The golden chare / of old&euml; conqueroures<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>olde</I>] R, old LH.</NOTE></L>
<L>Toward the tryumphe / for ther knyghtly deedis<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>Toward . . for</I>] Towardis . . of H, Towarde for R. <I>ther</I>] <I>om</I>. R.</NOTE></L>
