<LG N="8" TYPE="stanza">
<HEAD>(8)</HEAD>
<L N="50">&para; "Remembre of Ector / the Troian chaumpioun,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>Remembre</I>] Now H. <I>of</I>] LH, <I>om</I>. R.</NOTE></L>
