<L>In Duche, a <B>Rudder</B> is a knyght;<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>Duche, a Rudder</I>] whiche a Rider . callid H, Duche a rider is calld R (Hex|ham gives both <I>Rudder</I> and <I>Rider</I> in his Dutch Dict.).</NOTE></L>
