<L N="61">Caualaro<NOTE PLACE="foot">MS. Caualato, alterd to Caualaro, and with "Cavalero" in margin.</NOTE> / which, in that partie,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>which in</I>] LR, thurghout al H.</NOTE></L>
