<LG N="12" TYPE="stanza">
<HEAD>(12)</HEAD>
<L N="78">&para; "Tween to hyllis / the prophete Zacarie<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>to</I>] two HR. H has '&para; Montes erant &amp;c. Zakarie .iij<SUP>o</SUP>.' in margin.</NOTE></L>
