<LG N="13" TYPE="stanza">
<HEAD>(13)</HEAD>
<L N="85">&para; "The red hors / was tokne of hardynesse,<MILESTONE N="68b" UNIT="folio"><NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>was</I>] LR, was there H.</NOTE></L>
