<LG N="14" TYPE="stanza">
<HEAD>(14)</HEAD>
<L N="92">&para; "The many-fold coloures / to speke in generall,<NOTE PLACE="foot">(in margin) &para; Significant virtutes diuersas ad Miliciam pertinentes H.</NOTE></L>
