<LG N="15" TYPE="stanza">
<HEAD>(15)</HEAD>
<L N="99">&para; "Withouten hors / Iustis ne turney, att all<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>hors. .alle</I>] horses.Ioustes ne turnal H, horse iustes ne tournaill R.</NOTE></L>
