<L N="505">&para; This was the meene / tavoid&euml; first the stryves,<MILESTONE N="76" UNIT="folio"><NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>tavoide first</I>] to awoyde al HR. <I>the</I>] her R. <I>stryves</I>] H, strif La, her striues R.</NOTE></L>
