<L>Yit of ther wollis / be woven rich&euml; weedis,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>be woven</I>] bien wonder H.</NOTE></L>
<L N="559">Of smoth&euml; doun / maad pilwis for softnesse,</L>
<L>Fethirbeddis to sleepe, whan men dresse<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>whan men</I>] on whan men hem H.</NOTE></L>
<L>Toward Aurora / ageyn til thei arrise:<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>ageyn</I>] H. a gey La.</NOTE></L>
<L>Rolle vp this problem / thynk what it doth expresse:<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>what it</I>] it H.</NOTE></L>
