</LG>
<LG N="81" TYPE="stanza">
<HEAD>(81)</HEAD>
<L N="564">&para; The inward meenyng / to-forn as it is told,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>meenyng / to forne</I>] meanes . aforn H.</NOTE></L>
