<LG N="87" TYPE="stanza">
<HEAD>(87)</HEAD>
<L N="612">&para; Tweene riche &amp; poore / what is the difference,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>Tweene</I>] Atwene H.</NOTE></L>
