<PB REF="00000204.tif" N="154"></L>
<L>And<NOTE PLACE="foot">of</NOTE> all &thorn;e fylthe &thorn;at he was Inne.<NOTE PLACE="foot">his body with-in. L. adds: <Q><L>for meselle he was, as I seyde ere,</L><L>And afftyr, fayre man and clere</L></Q></NOTE></L>
