<L N="380"><NOTE PLACE="foot">L. inserts: <Q><L>A nodyr chappelle is in house,</L><L>there-in been Relykis precyouse:</L></Q></NOTE>A tabull &thorn;er ys, &thorn;at<NOTE PLACE="foot">the tabylle there-in</NOTE> men mey se</L>
