<L N="388">Also &thorn;er ben two tabeles, y vn&thorn;urstonde,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><Q><L>Above An Auter made of tree</L><L>lyche A tabylle, I telle thee;</L><L>vndyr the Awter, An Arche of stoone,</L><L>with holy Relykys many one.</L></Q></NOTE></L>
